  <description><![CDATA[<p>Perfectly located in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97}" title="Selva">Selva</a>, Hotel Linder is only a couple minutes’ walk (100m) from the main gondola that takes you to the Ciampinoi ski area. This family-run hotel offers exceptional service and is furnished with a mixture of traditional Val Gardena style and modern elements, providing our guests the perfect retreat after a day of skiing. Boasting a cosy lounge, a bar, a restaurant and the use of the facilities including indoor pool at their nearby sister hotel, Hotel Nives, at no extra cost. All rooms are comfortably furnished in contemporary Alpine style with balconies and larger superior rooms are south facing. The Linder's winning combination of modern comfort, central location and breathtaking views of the Dolomites, will turn your stay into a unique experience.</p>]]></description>
